title: Beyond the Horror: Murder House Episode 6
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: OITNB season 2 finale is the best finale ever, I stood up screaming at the tv "You go Ms Rosa!" Bawling with tears streaming down my face! So good.
Can't wait for Feud, I'm right with you, Mary! Beyond excited!
sorry, I missed your live show, but I'm watching now! missed you Casey!  Welcome Tammy! All of you are awesome!
Hey MaryGirl. I just want to say i learned a lot from your "how to write a novel" podcasts. And i will start to write my first movie script next friday.
description:
VIDEO CONTAINS SPOILERS FOR SEASON ONE, EPISODE 6 OF AMERICAN HORROR STORY!!!

Beyond the Horror: Murder House, is an unofficial American Horror Story Live After Show. Hosted by MaryGirl Moody, Maisie Andrews, Casey Soper, and Tami Sifford. We discuss and review each episode of American Horror Story Murder House. Join the Freaks of AHS on Facebook (link below), and Beyond the Horror.
